<nhs-page-title title="Buying Catalogue UI Components" />

<p>This WebApp contains the instructions on how to use the new UI Components in the Buying Catalogue UI.</p>
<p>The pages have been set up so that they use the Components themselves to create the pages.</p>
<p>reading the pages will tell you how to use them, while looking at their .cshtml files shows how they've been used to create these pages.</p>
<p>to find the components to use, use the menu on the left</p>

